{
  "stem": "24259.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, at that time, we, of course, were part of family discussions that took part-- of ways that my-- I also have an Uncle Max, my father's brother, who survived with his wife and son.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, they, they hid out in the woods during that whole time, actually dug holes in the woods.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and they survived also within that same area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, after the war we all stayed together and so forth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so certain family discussions and so forth would take place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, you would hear the various stories and information about how this person was killed and how that person was killed and so forth.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Always.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there's still a lot of crying that takes place now whenever certain things are recalled by my father and the rest of my-- my uncle and so forth, when we get together.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The memories are still very much etched in, in their minds, of course, in my father's mind now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Certain things.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think part of it, what little I remember, certainly during the war everything certainly after the war, I think it makes you feel different.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's kind of hard to put it into words.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think you feel Jewish, in a way, if you will, not in, in-- maybe in a bad way, it's just that you just feel different.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And certainly even being in the United States-- and I certainly have been fortunate to have a wonderful life in the United States and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I think you still feel a little different, as much as with the friends and people that you associate with.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always call it kind of thinking in Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
